      <span class="callout-label">Critical Distinction</span>
      <p>A 3PPS is <strong>not a pre-grant opposition</strong>. You cannot argue with the Examiner. You cannot participate in the proceedings. You submit documents, provide a factual description, pay the fee, and walk away. What the Examiner does with your submission is entirely at their discretion.</p>
